videos.headline: Jack Coan fires 29-yard TD pass to Lorenzo Styles Jr.
videos.description: Notre Dame strikes quickly in the Fiesta Bowl as Jack Coan slings a perfect pass to Lorenzo Styles Jr. for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jack Coan fires 29-yard TD pass to Lorenzo Styles Jr.) 2022/01/01 Esheet

videos.headline: Chris Tyree hauls in 53-yard TD catch
videos.description: Jack Coan tosses a pass over the blitz to a wide-open Chris Tyree, who races away untouched for the touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Chris Tyree hauls in 53-yard TD catch) 2022/01/01 Esheet

videos.headline: Jaden Bray breaks a tackle and dives in for a TD
videos.description: Jaden Bray gets the ball on a jet sweep and shakes a Notre Dame defender to reach the end zone.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Jaden Bray breaks a tackle and dives in for a TD) 2022/01/01 Esheet

videos.headline: Michael Mayer dives for the pylon and gets the Notre Dame TD
videos.description: Jack Coan tosses a play-action pass to Michael Mayer, who dives for the end zone on a 16-yard score.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michael Mayer dives for the pylon and gets the Notre Dame TD) 2022/01/01 Esheet

videos.headline: Michael Mayer scores his second TD for Notre Dame
videos.description: Michael Mayer makes a diving catch in the end zone for his second touchdown of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michael Mayer scores his second TD for Notre Dame) 2022/01/01 Esheet

videos.headline: Tay Martin gets both feet down in the back of the end zone
videos.description: Oklahoma State QB Spencer Sanders fires a 9-yard touchdown pass to Tay Martin in the final minute of the first half.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tay Martin gets both feet down in the back of the end zone) 2022/01/01 Esheet

videos.headline: Tay Martin makes another TD catch for Oklahoma State
videos.description: Spencer Sanders hits Tay Martin on a slant as Oklahoma State cuts Notre Dame's lead to seven.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tay Martin makes another TD catch for Oklahoma State) 2022/01/01 Esheet

videos.headline: Tay Martin scores his third TD of the game as OK State ties it up
videos.description: Spencer Sanders and Tay Martin connect for another touchdown as Oklahoma State ties the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tay Martin scores his third TD of the game as OK State ties it up) 2022/01/01 Esheet

videos.headline: OK State, Notre Dame exchange unbelievable takeaways
videos.description: Oklahoma State and Notre Dame force jaw-dropping fumbles on back-to-back possessions.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (OK State, Notre Dame exchange unbelievable takeaways) 2022/01/01 Esheet

videos.headline: Malcolm Rodriguez picks off Jack Coan in OK State territory
videos.description: Malcolm Rodriguez comes up with a huge interception for Oklahoma State as he picks off Jack Coan.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Malcolm Rodriguez picks off Jack Coan in OK State territory) 2022/01/01 Esheet

videos.headline: Tay Martin adds a wild catch to his 3 Fiesta Bowl TDs
videos.description: Tay Martin hangs in the air to make a spectacular catch on 3rd down for Oklahoma State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Tay Martin adds a wild catch to his 3 Fiesta Bowl TDs) 2022/01/01 Esheet

videos.headline: Notre Dame gets huge turnover late in 4th
videos.description: Notre Dame recovers the fumble late in the fourth quarter, giving the ball back to the offense.

videos.headline: Kevin Austin Jr. scores a late TD for Notre Dame
videos.description: Jack Coan hits Kevin Austin Jr. on a slant rout as Notre Dame cuts into Oklahoma State's late lead in the final seconds.

videos.headline: Tay Martin hauls in 3 TDs as Cowboys win the Fiesta Bowl
videos.description: Oklahoma State's Tay Martin goes for 104 yards and three touchdowns as the Cowboys beat Notre Dame in the Fiesta Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Tay Martin hauls in 3 TDs as Cowboys win the Fiesta Bowl) 2022/01/01 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Gundy: Fiesta Bowl comeback is biggest win in school history
videos.description: Mike Gundy raves about his team after a 21-point comeback win vs. Notre Dame in the PlayStation Fiesta Bowl.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (Gundy: Fiesta Bowl comeback is biggest win in school history) 2022/1/1
